comments: I noticed that Zetiko was spelt with a coe if the shape was yellow or grey. I learned the words by saying them out loud along with the computer. When I learned which was which I tested myself by not looking at the name being spelt out and just trying to say it out loud before the computer. I didn't take notes. I found the task hard at first when I was learning the difficult words, but then easy once I got to know them. I found the second part of the task harder and more frustrating, as I couldn't work out which colour my partner would pick for each shape.
